data.name: Hint_LegislationCelexNumber
data.value:
The Celex number is a unique identifier used on EUR-Lex - the official legal portal of the EU (e.g. 32001R0044). You can also enter partial numbers, replacing the missing characters with special symbols: * for multiple characters, ? for a single character.

The European Legislation Identifier (ELI) introduced by the EU Council uses ‘HTTP URIs’ to specifically identify all online legislative documents officially published across Europe.

Example: 32015R1733

data.name: UI_FullFeaturesMessage
data.value:
You have reached the limit of 5 documents that can be accessed for free.

With this Free Tour you have further access to the full texts of all decisions of the EU Court of Justice as well as the judgments of national courts published on the European Case-law Blog.

In order to get access to the texts of other documents, please click the button below and register to start your free trial. During the 5-day trial period, you will have access to the full content and functionality of the EuroCases service.

data.name: Hint_CaseLawCelexNumber
data.value:
The Celex number is a unique identifier used on EUR-Lex - the official legal portal of the EU (e.g. 62014CJ0032). You can also enter partial numbers, replacing the missing characters with special symbols: * for multiple characters, ? for a single character.

The European Case Law Identifier (ECLI) is a unified case law identifier introduced by the EU Council.

Example: 62014CJ0032

data.name: UI_FreeTour_InitialMessage
data.value:
With the EuroCases Free Tour you can freely access and view the full text of:

  • all EU legislative acts
  • all decisions of the EU Court of Justice
  • the judgments of national courts published on European Case-law Blog
  • up to five other documents (i.e. decisions of national courts and of the European court of Human Rights).

If you would like to enjoy access to the full content and functionality of EuroCases service, please click here to register and start your 5-day free trial.

data.name: UI_Fins_FullFeaturesMessage
data.value:
В настоящата Демо версия на Tax&Financial Standards, можете да получите безплатен достъп до актуалните консолидирани текстове на Финансово Право и практика на ЕС:
  • Регламенти
  • Директиви
  • Международни стандарти (МСС, МСФО и КРМСФО)
  • Европейска съдебна практика
  • Справочна финансова информация
  • Статистическа информация
  • Данъчна информация
  • Икономически речник
  • Валутни курсове и лихви
До 30.06.2016 ще имате допълнително свободен достъп до всички решения на на Съда на ЕС.

За да получите достъп до текстовете на други документи, както и да използвате пълната функционалност на продукта Tax&Financial Standards, моля, кликнете върху бутона по-долу и се регистрирайте, за да получите безплатен пробен период. По време на 5-дневния пробен период ще имате достъп до пълното съдържание и функционалност на продукта.

data.name: UI_TranslateSearchText_Hint
data.value: This is a prototype of cross-language search functionality. To use it, check the "Cross-lingual search" checkbox and type and execute a search query in the interface language.
